# Banner Images
This folder contains banner/carousel images for the hero section.

Recommended specifications:
- Resolution: 1920x800px (2.4:1 aspect ratio)
- Format: JPG or WebP
- File size: Max 500KB per image
- Quality: High (80-90%)

File naming convention:
- banner-01-photography.jpg
- banner-02-wedding.jpg
- banner-03-portrait.jpg
- banner-04-event.jpg